text: Novogumerovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Starogumerovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 121 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 27 km from Kushnarenkovo, 6 km from Starogumerovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Novogumerovo
